HEADWORD: Liberticide
<hw>Lib"er*ti*cide</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧b"⟦etil⟧r*t⟦icr⟧*s⟦imac⟧d)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>libertas</ets> liberty + <ets>caedere</ets>
to kill: cf. (for sense 2) F. <ets>liberticide</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
